ion is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/28/', '', 'Codeine, Oliceridine, Oxymorphone, Tapentadol, Meperidine, Butorphanol, Hydromorphone, Dezocine, Tramadol, Opium, Dextropropoxyphene, More', 'Paritaprevir, Glecaprevir, Simeprevir, Amprenavir, Cabotegravir, Valaciclovir, Zanamivir, Lenacapavir, Telaprevir, Velpatasvir, Etravirine, More', 1767369485);
